  "original_title": "\u0d86\u0dba\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db1\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dc0\u0daf\u0dcf\u0db1\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Corona is a risk again",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Director General of Health Services Dr. Asela Gunawardena said that it is important to get all four doses of the anti-covid vaccine as there is a risk of re-emergence of the covid disease.",
        "He also mentioned that there is a serious risk of the spread of Covid again with new varieties.",
        "Mr. Asela Gunawardena said that all those above the age of 60 and who wish to go abroad must receive this fourth dose of vaccination, and all those above the age of 20 should also receive it.",
        "The expert also said that by taking all 4 vaccines, the risk of getting infected with Covid-19 is reduced, the risk of getting into a severe condition and dying even if the disease is contracted is reduced.",
        "These vaccines can be obtained from all government hospitals, medical officer of health offices and designated vaccination centers, and depending on the situation in the country, vaccination dates may be limited or given only on designated days, so consult with the institutions to get vaccinated. Mr. Asela Gunawardena said that it should."
      ],
